// SOLID in action
// S: Separate responsibilities
// O: Add new PaymentMethod without touching core logic
// L: Subtypes replace base types without breaking
// I: Split IPrinter, IScanner, IFax
// D: Inject IPaymentService into dependent classes

// These principles together lead to clean, modular, and testable code.

